{
  "video_id": "JiwZQNYlGQI",
  "title": "Failing at Normal: An ADHD Success Story | Jessica McCabe | TEDxBratislava",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Leonardo Silva Reviewer: Mile Živković"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 8202.0,
      "end_time": 9857.0,
      "text": "Hello, brains!"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 10960.0,
      "end_time": 13402.0,
      "text": "I say that to you because, if you think about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13402.0,
      "end_time": 16332.0,
      "text": "it wasn&#39;t really you that decided to come here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16332.0,
      "end_time": 17813.0,
      "text": "It was your brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 18151.0,
      "end_time": 22503.0,
      "text": "And whether you decided to walk, or drive, take a taxi, or ride a bike,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 22503.0,
      "end_time": 25620.0,
      "text": "that decision was made by your brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25620.0,
      "end_time": 29464.0,
      "text": "Behavior, all behavior, is affected by the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 30323.0,
      "end_time": 32328.0,
      "text": "This is a story about my brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 33192.0,
      "end_time": 34774.0,
      "text": "So, I was a smart kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 34774.0,
      "end_time": 38930.0,
      "text": "By 18 months, I was speaking in full sentences."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38930.0,
      "end_time": 42824.0,
      "text": "By third grade, I was scoring post-high school on standardized tests."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42824.0,
      "end_time": 46565.0,
      "text": "I had, as all my teachers agreed, so much potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47623.0,
      "end_time": 49543.0,
      "text": "I was also struggling."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49543.0,
      "end_time": 52763.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t have many, any, friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52764.0,
      "end_time": 54240.0,
      "text": "outside of books."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54565.0,
      "end_time": 57564.0,
      "text": "I was easily overwhelmed. I spaced out in class."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57564.0,
      "end_time": 60462.0,
      "text": "I lost things constantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60462.0,
      "end_time": 64244.0,
      "text": "And trying to get my brain to focus on anything I wasn&#39;t excited about"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 64244.0,
      "end_time": 67450.0,
      "text": "was like trying to nail jello to the wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68354.0,
      "end_time": 71840.0,
      "text": "But I was smart, so nobody was worried."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71383.0,
      "end_time": 72827.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t until middle school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72828.0,
      "end_time": 76136.0,
      "text": "when I was responsible for getting myself to classes on time"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76136.0,
      "end_time": 78540.0,
      "text": "and remembering to bring my own homework,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78550.0,
      "end_time": 82885.0,
      "text": "that being smart wasn&#39;t enough anymore, and my grades started to suffer."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83686.0,
      "end_time": 87570.0,
      "text": "My mom took me to the doctor and, after a comprehensive evaluation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87570.0,
      "end_time": 90606.0,
      "text": "I was diagnosed with  attention deficit hyperactivity disorder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90606.0,
      "end_time": 91945.0,
      "text": "ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91945.0,
      "end_time": 95467.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re not familiar with ADHD, it has three primary characteristics:"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95467.0,
      "end_time": 98985.0,
      "text": "inattention, impulsivity,  and hyperactivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99877.0,
      "end_time": 104437.0,
      "text": "Some people with ADHD have more of the inattentive presentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104437.0,
      "end_time": 107458.0,
      "text": "Those are the daydreamers, the space cadets."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107458.0,
      "end_time": 110848.0,
      "text": "Some have more of the hyperactive-impulsive presentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110848.0,
      "end_time": 113298.0,
      "text": "Those are the kids that usually get diagnosed early."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113298.0,
      "end_time": 114885.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115915.0,
      "end_time": 118795.0,
      "text": "But the most common presentation is a combination of both."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 119795.0,
      "end_time": 121446.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121446.0,
      "end_time": 126347.0,
      "text": "My doctor and my parents decided that, given my shiny, new diagnosis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 126347.0,
      "end_time": 131329.0,
      "text": "maybe stimulant medication would succeed where spankings and lectures had failed."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131330.0,
      "end_time": 134225.0,
      "text": "So I tried it, and it worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134979.0,
      "end_time": 136711.0,
      "text": "The first time I took my medication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 136711.0,
      "end_time": 138866.0,
      "text": "it was like putting on glasses"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138866.0,
      "end_time": 142119.0,
      "text": "and realizing I could see without squinting."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 142589.0,
      "end_time": 144400.0,
      "text": "I could focus."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146400.0,
      "end_time": 149955.0,
      "text": "And without changing anything, my GPA went up a full point."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152350.0,
      "end_time": 153778.0,
      "text": "Honestly, it was kind of miraculous."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 153778.0,
      "end_time": 157220.0,
      "text": "By 14, I had friends that liked me."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 157220.0,
      "end_time": 160970.0,
      "text": "By 15, I had published my first poem."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 160970.0,
      "end_time": 161784.0,
      "text": "I got a boyfriend."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 161784.0,
      "end_time": 164988.0,
      "text": "By 17, I knew I wanted to be a journalist."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 164988.0,
      "end_time": 169643.0,
      "text": "My local college had a program that would guarantee admission to USC."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 169929.0,
      "end_time": 172250.0,
      "text": "They had a really great  journalism program."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172250.0,
      "end_time": 176227.0,
      "text": "So, I signed up at my local college and I started taking classes."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176650.0,
      "end_time": 178481.0,
      "text": "I moved in with my boyfriend."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 178840.0,
      "end_time": 181320.0,
      "text": "Things were going great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 181320.0,
      "end_time": 182674.0,
      "text": "until they weren&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 183294.0,
      "end_time": 185869.0,
      "text": "I started having trouble making it to class on time."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 185869.0,
      "end_time": 188530.0,
      "text": "I aced a statistics course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 188530.0,
      "end_time": 192200.0,
      "text": "but I forgot to sign up in time, so I never got the credit."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192721.0,
      "end_time": 195790.0,
      "text": "I took classes so I could help my boyfriend with his career,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 195790.0,
      "end_time": 198442.0,
      "text": "but I completely lost sight of mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 200679.0,
      "end_time": 202760.0,
      "text": "I never made it to USC."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 203620.0,
      "end_time": 207910.0,
      "text": "By 21, I dropped out of college and moved back home."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 208602.0,
      "end_time": 214428.0,
      "text": "Over the next ten years, I started and quit, or was fired from, 15 jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 214763.0,
      "end_time": 216776.0,
      "text": "I ruined my credit."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216776.0,
      "end_time": 218593.0,
      "text": "I got married,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 218593.0,
      "end_time": 220623.0,
      "text": "and was divorced within a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 222610.0,
      "end_time": 223862.0,
      "text": "At this point, I was 32,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223862.0,
      "end_time": 227355.0,
      "text": "and I had no idea what I was doing with my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 227355.0,
      "end_time": 231204.0,
      "text": "besides reading self-help books that didn&#39;t seem to be helping."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 232710.0,
      "end_time": 234413.0,
      "text": "What happened to all that potential?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 234413.0,
      "end_time": 240720.0,
      "text": "Was I not trying? No! I worked harder than anyone I knew."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 240720.0,
      "end_time": 242364.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t even have time for friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 242364.0,
      "end_time": 244128.0,
      "text": "I was that busy."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 245804.0,
      "end_time": 248589.0,
      "text": "I had potential, though."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 250400.0,
      "end_time": 252416.0,
      "text": "So, my failure was clearly my fault."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 253870.0,
      "end_time": 255392.0,
      "text": "I just hadn&#39;t done what I need to do to reach it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 255392.0,
      "end_time": 259197.0,
      "text": "and, honestly, I was tired of trying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 260512.0,
      "end_time": 263253.0,
      "text": "putting more effort into life than everyone else"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 263254.0,
      "end_time": 265799.0,
      "text": "and falling farther and farther behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 267354.0,
      "end_time": 270200.0,
      "text": "At this point, I could have given up on myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 270200.0,
      "end_time": 274933.0,
      "text": "I could have decided that everyone who&#39;d thought I had potential was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 275464.0,
      "end_time": 276753.0,
      "text": "But I didn&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 276753.0,
      "end_time": 281540.0,
      "text": "because I knew that it was my behavior that had gotten me here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 281540.0,
      "end_time": 283974.0,
      "text": "and behavior is affected by the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 283974.0,
      "end_time": 286462.0,
      "text": "and my brain has ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 287204.0,
      "end_time": 289723.0,
      "text": "Looking at my behavior, I knew:"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 289723.0,
      "end_time": 292973.0,
      "text": "even with medication, even as an adult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 292973.0,
      "end_time": 295145.0,
      "text": "my ADHD was still interfering with my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 295145.0,
      "end_time": 297193.0,
      "text": "and what I needed to know was how and why,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 297194.0,
      "end_time": 300176.0,
      "text": "and, more importantly, what could I do about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 300176.0,
      "end_time": 302229.0,
      "text": "I started to do some research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 302229.0,
      "end_time": 305195.0,
      "text": "and I found a lot of great information."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 305195.0,
      "end_time": 308635.0,
      "text": "I found a lot of bad information too, but that&#39;s another talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 308635.0,
      "end_time": 311970.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s good information out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 311970.0,
      "end_time": 316660.0,
      "text": "Websites, podcasts, talks, by researchers and medical professionals;"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 316346.0,
      "end_time": 318486.0,
      "text": "books that would have been  way more helpful"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 318486.0,
      "end_time": 322146.0,
      "text": "than the self-help books I&#39;d been using that were clearly written for normal -"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 322146.0,
      "end_time": 325367.0,
      "text": "well, there&#39;s no normal - neurotypical brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 326295.0,
      "end_time": 329217.0,
      "text": "A lot of what I found, though, was either super technical"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 329217.0,
      "end_time": 332187.0,
      "text": "or seemed like it was written for parents and teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 332187.0,
      "end_time": 334791.0,
      "text": "trying to deal with ADHD kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 334791.0,
      "end_time": 337418.0,
      "text": "There wasn&#39;t a lot that seemed intended for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 337418.0,
      "end_time": 339946.0,
      "text": "the people who have ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 340606.0,
      "end_time": 342804.0,
      "text": "So, I started a YouTube channel."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 343937.0,
      "end_time": 346450.0,
      "text": "I had no idea how to start a YouTube channel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 346450.0,
      "end_time": 347967.0,
      "text": "but I started a YouTube channel."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 347967.0,
      "end_time": 350970.0,
      "text": "I almost called it \"How Not To ADHD,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 350980.0,
      "end_time": 352258.0,
      "text": "because that was about all I knew at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 352258.0,
      "end_time": 354498.0,
      "text": "But my boyfriend, Edward, talked me out of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 354499.0,
      "end_time": 357248.0,
      "text": "It turns out lots of people need help understanding ADHD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 357248.0,
      "end_time": 360308.0,
      "text": "including, maybe especially, those who actually have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 360309.0,
      "end_time": 361739.0,
      "text": "I was no exception."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 361739.0,
      "end_time": 364327.0,
      "text": "I thought ADHD was kind of the same for everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 364327.0,
      "end_time": 366799.0,
      "text": "I thought it was mostly about getting distracted."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 366799.0,
      "end_time": 371750.0,
      "text": "I thought having ADHD was maybe the reason that I was failing at life."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 373100.0,
      "end_time": 376590.0,
      "text": "And I thought I was what needed to change, in order to be successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 377480.0,
      "end_time": 380900.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t be successful and still be me."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 381237.0,
      "end_time": 383800.0,
      "text": "Spoilers: I was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 383689.0,
      "end_time": 387319.0,
      "text": "So, let&#39;s go back for a second, let&#39;s go back to what brought us here today:"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 387319.0,
      "end_time": 388751.0,
      "text": "the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 389199.0,
      "end_time": 393680.0,
      "text": "Understanding the brain you&#39;re working with, it turns out, is kind of important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 393680.0,
      "end_time": 397445.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s true whether that brain is your employee&#39;s, your student&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 397446.0,
      "end_time": 400335.0,
      "text": "your kid&#39;s, your significant other&#39;s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 400335.0,
      "end_time": 401705.0,
      "text": "or your own."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 402208.0,
      "end_time": 406716.0,
      "text": "ADHD affects between 5 and 8% of the global population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 406716.0,
      "end_time": 408883.0,
      "text": "which means, statistically speaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 408883.0,
      "end_time": 413777.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s between 37 and 60 of us just in this room."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 416543.0,
      "end_time": 419999.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t tell who we are just by looking, but it&#39;s fun to watch you try."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 419999.0,
      "end_time": 421394.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 422500.0,
      "end_time": 425682.0,
      "text": "So, at some point, you&#39;re going to meet someone with ADHD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 426531.0,
      "end_time": 429562.0,
      "text": "work with them, give birth to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 429562.0,
      "end_time": 431249.0,
      "text": "or fall in love with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 431601.0,
      "end_time": 434550.0,
      "text": "Chances are you already have."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 434550.0,
      "end_time": 437321.0,
      "text": "And, at some point, you&#39;re going to ask yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 437321.0,
      "end_time": 439960.0,
      "text": "\"What is going on in their brain?!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 440930.0,
      "end_time": 445871.0,
      "text": "So, after two years of learning about ADHD and a lifetime of experience with it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 445871.0,
      "end_time": 449600.0,
      "text": "after having the honor of connecting with researchers, and doctors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 449600.0,
      "end_time": 454529.0,
      "text": "and ADHD experts, and tens of thousands of ADHD brains all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 455241.0,
      "end_time": 459188.0,
      "text": "what can I tell you to help you understand ADHD?"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 459572.0,
      "end_time": 462505.0,
      "text": "By the way, many of them helped with this talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 463302.0,
      "end_time": 464875.0,
      "text": "First of all, it&#39;s real."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 465113.0,
      "end_time": 467273.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not bad parenting or lack of discipline."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 467273.0,
      "end_time": 470251.0,
      "text": "ADHD is a neurodevelopmental disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 470841.0,
      "end_time": 473973.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s currently the most well-researched mental condition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 473973.0,
      "end_time": 476753.0,
      "text": "and there are actually measurable differences in the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 476753.0,
      "end_time": 481253.0,
      "text": "These differences are larger in children, but, for most people, they never go away."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 481254.0,
      "end_time": 484276.0,
      "text": "In other words, adults have ADHD too."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 485162.0,
      "end_time": 487623.0,
      "text": "While rates of ADHD diagnosis are increasing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 487624.0,
      "end_time": 491404.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not because of an increase in sugar or technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 491404.0,
      "end_time": 494534.0,
      "text": "or lack of spanking;"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 494823.0,
      "end_time": 495943.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 495944.0,
      "end_time": 499804.0,
      "text": "any more than people drowning in swimming pools is because of Nicolas Cage."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 499804.0,
      "end_time": 502337.0,
      "text": "Correlation does not equal causation."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 503453.0,
      "end_time": 504996.0,
      "text": "Those are real numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 504996.0,
      "end_time": 506334.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 506334.0,
      "end_time": 509995.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s from both an increase in understanding that ADHD exists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 509995.0,
      "end_time": 513774.0,
      "text": "that girls, adults, and gifted students can have it too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 513774.0,
      "end_time": 515601.0,
      "text": "and ironically a lack of understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 515601.0,
      "end_time": 519995.0,
      "text": "that being hyper, misbehaving, or struggling in school"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 520495.0,
      "end_time": 523268.0,
      "text": "does not mean you have ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 524915.0,
      "end_time": 527262.0,
      "text": "ADHD is more serious than I realized."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 527693.0,
      "end_time": 532215.0,
      "text": "The primary characteristics - inattention, impulsivity, and hyperactivity -"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 532215.0,
      "end_time": 535255.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t sound all that serious, and I didn&#39;t think that they were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 535255.0,
      "end_time": 540226.0,
      "text": "but, in real life, they translate to people getting into more accidents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 540226.0,
      "end_time": 543942.0,
      "text": "being more likely to get fired, get divorced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 543942.0,
      "end_time": 546928.0,
      "text": "significantly more likely to struggle with addiction."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 547653.0,
      "end_time": 550337.0,
      "text": "I learned that ADHD is on a spectrum."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 550337.0,
      "end_time": 552499.0,
      "text": "Raise your hand if you&#39;ve ever lost your keys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 552499.0,
      "end_time": 554673.0,
      "text": "or spaced out in the middle of a lecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 555650.0,
      "end_time": 556606.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re not raising your hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 556606.0,
      "end_time": 559486.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to assume you spaced out in the middle of this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 559486.0,
      "end_time": 560626.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 560626.0,
      "end_time": 564718.0,
      "text": "The thing is, while everyone experiences ADHD symptoms sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 564718.0,
      "end_time": 567445.0,
      "text": "an actual diagnosis is based on how many of those symptoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 567446.0,
      "end_time": 571731.0,
      "text": "significantly and chronically impair multiple aspects of your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 571977.0,
      "end_time": 574347.0,
      "text": "Just like you can get sad and not have depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 574347.0,
      "end_time": 576709.0,
      "text": "you can get distracted and not have ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 576709.0,
      "end_time": 579827.0,
      "text": "And just like you can have mild depression or severe depression,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 579827.0,
      "end_time": 582557.0,
      "text": "ADHD can range from mild to severe."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 582557.0,
      "end_time": 586210.0,
      "text": "I also learned ADHD is a terrible name for ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 586210.0,
      "end_time": 588598.0,
      "text": "It creates a lot of confusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 588598.0,
      "end_time": 591469.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t have a deficit of attention!"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 591470.0,
      "end_time": 595226.0,
      "text": "What we have trouble with is regulating our attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 595226.0,
      "end_time": 597177.0,
      "text": "As ADHD coach Brett Thornhill puts it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 597177.0,
      "end_time": 600338.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s like your brain keeps switching between 30 different channels"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 600338.0,
      "end_time": 602721.0,
      "text": "and somebody else has the remote."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 603468.0,
      "end_time": 605507.0,
      "text": "Sometimes we have trouble focusing at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 605508.0,
      "end_time": 608918.0,
      "text": "and other times we get stuck on a channel and can&#39;t pull ourselves away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 608918.0,
      "end_time": 611690.0,
      "text": "which in real life might seem we don&#39;t want to do homework"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 611690.0,
      "end_time": 615499.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;d rather play video games, and short, sometimes that&#39;s the case."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 615809.0,
      "end_time": 619226.0,
      "text": "But the truth is there are plenty of times we want to able to focus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 619226.0,
      "end_time": 621459.0,
      "text": "we try, and we just can&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 621459.0,
      "end_time": 623579.0,
      "text": "Current understanding is that this difficulty"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 623580.0,
      "end_time": 627107.0,
      "text": "has to do with the way our brains produce and metabolize neurotransmitters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 627107.0,
      "end_time": 629559.0,
      "text": "like dopamine and norepinephrine."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 630108.0,
      "end_time": 631949.0,
      "text": "I learned ADHD is highly treatable."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 631950.0,
      "end_time": 634821.0,
      "text": "Stimulant medication boosts these neurotransmitters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 634821.0,
      "end_time": 637221.0,
      "text": "which is why it helps us focus."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 637221.0,
      "end_time": 641499.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very effective for around 80% of people with ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 642300.0,
      "end_time": 644103.0,
      "text": "And I learned that  medication isn&#39;t enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 644104.0,
      "end_time": 645940.0,
      "text": "ADHD affects much more than our focus."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 645940.0,
      "end_time": 648714.0,
      "text": "It impairs executive functions like planning, prioritizing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 648714.0,
      "end_time": 651897.0,
      "text": "and our ability to sustain effort toward a goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 651897.0,
      "end_time": 655790.0,
      "text": "It affects our ability to regulate our emotions, our behavior, our sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 655790.0,
      "end_time": 658459.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not one program in our brain that works differently;"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 658460.0,
      "end_time": 660360.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the whole operating system."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 660360.0,
      "end_time": 662645.0,
      "text": "It can affect every aspect of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 662645.0,
      "end_time": 665385.0,
      "text": "And there are a ton of strategies out there that can help."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 665385.0,
      "end_time": 668920.0,
      "text": "Cognitive behavioral therapy, coaching, even meditation or regular exercise"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 668920.0,
      "end_time": 671847.0,
      "text": "can help make a huge difference understanding your brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 672892.0,
      "end_time": 676341.0,
      "text": "I knew I had trouble focusing, and I knew my medication helped with that."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 676341.0,
      "end_time": 679154.0,
      "text": "What I didn&#39;t know was that getting overwhelmed all the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 679154.0,
      "end_time": 682780.0,
      "text": "had to do with poor working memory, and that making lists helps;"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 683300.0,
      "end_time": 686872.0,
      "text": "or that the reason I ran late all the time wasn&#39;t because I didn&#39;t care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 686872.0,
      "end_time": 690203.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s because ADHD&#39;ers have a skewed sense of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 690203.0,
      "end_time": 693560.0,
      "text": "and that using a timer could teach me how long things actually take."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 693561.0,
      "end_time": 696722.0,
      "text": "Mostly, I expected to learn what I actually learned:"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 696722.0,
      "end_time": 698703.0,
      "text": "that ADHD is real;"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 698703.0,
      "end_time": 700362.0,
      "text": "addressing it is important;"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 700362.0,
      "end_time": 702243.0,
      "text": "and medication is not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 702730.0,
      "end_time": 704781.0,
      "text": "What I didn&#39;t expect to learn:"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 705375.0,
      "end_time": 706977.0,
      "text": "that I wasn&#39;t alone;"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 707492.0,
      "end_time": 709592.0,
      "text": "I had an ADHD tribe;"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 709592.0,
      "end_time": 711982.0,
      "text": "what a difference it would make to connect with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 711982.0,
      "end_time": 714184.0,
      "text": "There are people with ADHD in every country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 714184.0,
      "end_time": 716613.0,
      "text": "every culture across the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 716614.0,
      "end_time": 718684.0,
      "text": "Yes, even in France."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 719104.0,
      "end_time": 720763.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 721684.0,
      "end_time": 723242.0,
      "text": "And this tribe is awesome."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 723243.0,
      "end_time": 725730.0,
      "text": "Comparing myself to people with neurotypical brains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 725730.0,
      "end_time": 727216.0,
      "text": "I felt really bad about myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 727216.0,
      "end_time": 730663.0,
      "text": "Why couldn&#39;t I keep my house clean or finish a project in time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 730663.0,
      "end_time": 733372.0,
      "text": "instead of waiting till the very last second?"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 734850.0,
      "end_time": 736777.0,
      "text": "But seeing the positives in fellow ADHD brains"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 736777.0,
      "end_time": 739211.0,
      "text": "helped me recognize and appreciate my own strengths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 739211.0,
      "end_time": 742487.0,
      "text": "ones I couldn&#39;t see when I was just staring at my weaknesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 742487.0,
      "end_time": 745430.0,
      "text": "which is what I&#39;d been doing for decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 745430.0,
      "end_time": 750286.0,
      "text": "But ADHD brains have a lot to offer the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 750286.0,
      "end_time": 753643.0,
      "text": "We tend to be generous, funny, creative."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 753644.0,
      "end_time": 757746.0,
      "text": "ADHD&#39;ers are 300% more likely to start their own business."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 757746.0,
      "end_time": 759496.0,
      "text": "We not only think outside the box;"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 759496.0,
      "end_time": 761737.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re often not even aware that there is a box."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 761737.0,
      "end_time": 763285.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 763765.0,
      "end_time": 766105.0,
      "text": "We may struggle when our brains aren&#39;t engaged,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 766105.0,
      "end_time": 769855.0,
      "text": "but ADHD brains are great at tackling tasks that are urgent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 769855.0,
      "end_time": 772670.0,
      "text": "working with ideas that are new,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 772670.0,
      "end_time": 774975.0,
      "text": "wrestling with problems that are challenging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 774975.0,
      "end_time": 778856.0,
      "text": "and dedicating themselves to projects that are of personal interest."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 779608.0,
      "end_time": 783266.0,
      "text": "This YouTube career I&#39;d stumbled into was all of those things."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 783737.0,
      "end_time": 785707.0,
      "text": "At 32, I was divorced, miserable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 785707.0,
      "end_time": 787887.0,
      "text": "and had no idea what I was doing with my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 787887.0,
      "end_time": 792708.0,
      "text": "At 33, I&#39;d started my own business, and was connecting with ADHD experts."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 793746.0,
      "end_time": 796740.0,
      "text": "By now, at 34,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 797210.0,
      "end_time": 799758.0,
      "text": "I have a team of volunteers helping with the channel."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 799758.0,
      "end_time": 803855.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m engaged to this amazing man who helps me produce the channel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 803855.0,
      "end_time": 807110.0,
      "text": "works right alongside with me, is doing the slides right now -"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 808647.0,
      "end_time": 811529.0,
      "text": "and, as we discovered, also has ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 811529.0,
      "end_time": 813128.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 813128.0,
      "end_time": 814969.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m working on reaching out to schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 814969.0,
      "end_time": 817388.0,
      "text": "so that kids don&#39;t have to wait until they&#39;re 32"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 817388.0,
      "end_time": 819509.0,
      "text": "to learn about their brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 819509.0,
      "end_time": 824380.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m doing my very first TEDx talk here with you today."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 824380.0,
      "end_time": 826701.0,
      "text": "(Cheers) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 832439.0,
      "end_time": 834194.0,
      "text": "But wait! There&#39;s more! Wait."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 834194.0,
      "end_time": 835851.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 835851.0,
      "end_time": 838849.0,
      "text": "That did sound like the end of the speech. I&#39;m sorry, it&#39;s not."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 838849.0,
      "end_time": 840640.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 840640.0,
      "end_time": 843129.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m happier and more successful than I&#39;ve ever been in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 843129.0,
      "end_time": 846694.0,
      "text": "So, what happened? How did I reach my potential?"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 847159.0,
      "end_time": 851760.0,
      "text": "Three things: one, I learned about my brain, my ADHD brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 851760.0,
      "end_time": 855620.0,
      "text": "both on my own and by connecting with others who have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 855441.0,
      "end_time": 858551.0,
      "text": "If you judge a fish by its ability to climb a tree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 858551.0,
      "end_time": 861160.0,
      "text": "it will live its whole life believing it is stupid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 861160.0,
      "end_time": 863230.0,
      "text": "unless it happens to chat  with another fish"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 863230.0,
      "end_time": 866428.0,
      "text": "and realizes fish aren&#39;t great at climbing trees, and that&#39;s okay,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 866428.0,
      "end_time": 868430.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s plenty of ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 869288.0,
      "end_time": 871539.0,
      "text": "Two, in learning about my brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 871539.0,
      "end_time": 875840.0,
      "text": "I found and stumbled into a job that engages it."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 875691.0,
      "end_time": 879861.0,
      "text": "If you spend all your time trying to get a fish to able to climb a tree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 879861.0,
      "end_time": 881980.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll never see how far it can swim."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 882571.0,
      "end_time": 886502.0,
      "text": "It turns out I can be me and still be successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 887171.0,
      "end_time": 889273.0,
      "text": "I just had to find my ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 889862.0,
      "end_time": 893680.0,
      "text": "Three, I learned strategies for challenges I still face."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 893680.0,
      "end_time": 896510.0,
      "text": "I have no fish analogy for this one, I&#39;m sorry."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 896520.0,
      "end_time": 897300.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 897300.0,
      "end_time": 898843.0,
      "text": "I guess I learned how to swim."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 900102.0,
      "end_time": 902536.0,
      "text": "Once you know what your brain&#39;s challenges are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 902537.0,
      "end_time": 904402.0,
      "text": "you can find solutions to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 904402.0,
      "end_time": 909279.0,
      "text": "Once you look past the stereotypes and assumptions about people with ADHD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 909279.0,
      "end_time": 913680.0,
      "text": "and dig deeper, you learn what ADHD actually is."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 913673.0,
      "end_time": 917262.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not people who won&#39;t stop fidgeting, or getting distracted."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 917262.0,
      "end_time": 920420.0,
      "text": "It is brains that are chronically underaroused,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 920420.0,
      "end_time": 924229.0,
      "text": "trying to get the basic level of stimulation all brains need."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 924843.0,
      "end_time": 927492.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not about procrastinating or not caring."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 927493.0,
      "end_time": 931106.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s having executive function deficits that make it hard to get started."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 931423.0,
      "end_time": 934773.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not people being lazy or not trying enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 934773.0,
      "end_time": 937441.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kids and adults struggling to succeed"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 937441.0,
      "end_time": 940710.0,
      "text": "with a brain that doesn&#39;t always want to cooperate"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 940710.0,
      "end_time": 942675.0,
      "text": "in a society that wasn&#39;t built for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 943932.0,
      "end_time": 946406.0,
      "text": "Society is our user&#39;s manual."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 947834.0,
      "end_time": 951584.0,
      "text": "We learn how our brains and bodies work by watching those around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 952250.0,
      "end_time": 955456.0,
      "text": "And, when yours works differently, it can feel like you&#39;re broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 955873.0,
      "end_time": 958884.0,
      "text": "So, what I&#39;m trying to do is reach out to these people"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 958884.0,
      "end_time": 962300.0,
      "text": "wherever they are in the world, and tell them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 963614.0,
      "end_time": 966814.0,
      "text": "\"You are not weird. You are not stupid."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 966814.0,
      "end_time": 971424.0,
      "text": "You do not need to try harder. You are not a failed version of normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 972315.0,
      "end_time": 975625.0,
      "text": "You are different, you are beautiful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 975625.0,
      "end_time": 977320.0,
      "text": "and you are not alone.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 978556.0,
      "end_time": 981995.0,
      "text": "If you don&#39;t ADHD yourself, chances are you know somebody who does."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 981995.0,
      "end_time": 986444.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re your employee, your boss, your friend, they&#39;re in this room."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 986444.0,
      "end_time": 989170.0,
      "text": "I hope this talk helps you understand them better."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 989551.0,
      "end_time": 991664.0,
      "text": "If you do have ADHD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 992836.0,
      "end_time": 994676.0,
      "text": "welcome to the tribe."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 996246.0,
      "end_time": 999117.0,
      "text": "(Applause) (Cheers)"
    }
  ]
}